window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>From USA Today bestselling romance author Dakota Davies comes an all new small town opposites attract romance about a runaway bride and the mysterious outsider who risks it all to protect her.</p> <p>The rules were simple. Ditch my past for a fresh start in Finn River. Keep my head down, work hard, and stay out of trouble.</p> <p>But trouble has a name: Kirilee St. Claire. She’s sweet and feisty, with legs for days and a wicked stubborn streak that turns my crank. She’s also my new boss’s daughter, wealthy, educated, and way out of my league.</p> <p>And…engaged to a jerk.</p> <p>So when she begs for my help tackling a set of secret goals–a mischievous little bucket list–before she ties the knot, even though it’s reckless and ballsy for us both, I’m all in.</p> <p>Yet the more time we spend as partners in crime, the crazier things get. Though we stay safely in the friend zone, I fall for her in a hundred ways. And by way she’s looking at me, I'm not alone. How can I convince her to say goodbye to Mr. Wrong, and take a walk on the wild side with me instead?</p> <p>And when the shadows from my past find me, do I hide from the truth, or risk it all for my reckless heart?</p> <p>Author's note: A mysterious stranger with a heart of gold, a small-town sweetheart finding her courage, and a quirky mountain community rallying for love. Add a fiercely loyal found family, hilarious hijinks, plenty of heat, and a shocking twist, and you have a recipe for a wild and reckless ride.</p> <p>Love Me Reckless is a standalone small town contemporary romance novel and book 2 in the unforgettable Love Me Dangerous series.</p>"; 
